    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required credibility level. One factor (Test conditions) achieved level 2 against a required level 3 due to single test condition; this is accepted based on compensating evidence from multi-laboratory replication and the conservative nature of the ASTM F1717 standard condition relative to in vivo loading. Validation results demonstrate all QoIs within pre-specified acceptance bounds across N=11 specimens. Overall credibility is sufficient to support the intended use decision.",
